Question:
An error occurred when an AI model in ONNX format was converted using DRP-AI Translator. 
What should I do next?
Answer:
Determine the cause of the error from the error code. 
If you are using an operator that is not supported by the DRP-AI, replace it with another operator. 
For the supported operators, refer to the User's Manual for DRP-AI Translator.
Suitable Products
RZ/V2L, RZ/V2M
